@title Modern ERC-20 implementation.
  @dev   Acknowledgements to Solmate, OpenZeppelin, and DSS for inspiring this code.

devdoc.details: Acknowledgements to Solmate, OpenZeppelin, and DSS for inspiring this code.

approve(address,uint256).details: Function that allows one account to set the allowance of another account over their tokens.          Emits an {Approval} event.

params.amount_: Amount of tokens that have been approved.
params.spender_: Account that tokens are approved for.

returns.success_: Boolean indicating whether the operation succeeded.

params.decimals_: The decimal precision used by the token.

decreaseAllowance(address,uint256).details: Function that allows one account to decrease the allowance of another account over their tokens.          Emits an {Approval} event.

params.spender_: Account that tokens are approved for.

returns.success_: Boolean indicating whether the operation succeeded.

increaseAllowance(address,uint256).details: Function that allows one account to increase the allowance of another account over their tokens.          Emits an {Approval} event.

params.spender_: Account that tokens are approved for.

returns.success_: Boolean indicating whether the operation succeeded.

params.deadline_: Deadline after which the permit is invalid.
params.owner_: Owner address that signed the permit.

transfer(address,uint256).details: Moves an amount of tokens from `msg.sender` to a specified account.          Emits a {Transfer} event.

params.amount_: Amount of tokens that are transferred.

returns.success_: Boolean indicating whether the operation succeeded.

transferFrom(address,address,uint256).details: Moves a pre-approved amount of tokens from a sender to a specified account.          Emits a {Transfer} event.          Emits an {Approval} event.

params.amount_: Amount of tokens that are transferred.
params.owner_: Account that tokens are moving from.

returns.success_: Boolean indicating whether the operation succeeded.

allowance.details: Returns the allowance that one account has given another over their tokens.

params.owner_: Account that tokens are approved from.
params.spender_: Account that tokens are approved for.

allowance.return: Allowance that one account has given another over their tokens.

returns._0: Allowance that one account has given another over their tokens.

balanceOf.details: Returns the amount of tokens owned by a given account.
balanceOf.return: Amount of tokens owned by a given account.

returns._0: Amount of tokens owned by a given account.

decimals.details: Returns the decimal precision used by the token.
decimals.return: The decimal precision used by the token.

returns._0: The decimal precision used by the token.

name.details: Returns the name of the token.

nonces.details: Returns the nonce for the given owner.

params.owner_: The address of the owner account.

nonces.return: The nonce for the given owner.

returns._0: The nonce for the given owner.

symbol.details: Returns the symbol of the token.

totalSupply.details: Returns the total amount of tokens in existence.
totalSupply.return: The total amount of tokens in existence.

returns._0: The total amount of tokens in existence.
